Technical Design / Pre Sales Engineer
Confidential Company - ,
Date Posted: 2014/05/04 13:31:09
Ref. JB3047118
Job Description
Assist & provide sales support & application design of low current & security systems to customers.
Prepare bill of quantities for clients.
Plan & design low current & security systems, check design complatibility based upon client's enquiry.
Comminicate with clients for relevant inpouts for pricing purpose.
Build & maintain customer relationship to ensure consumer satisfaction.
Prepare technical submittals for project design.
Contact vendor & manufacturer for follow ups on requested quotes & designs.
Skills
Degree / Diploma in Electronics Engineering / Electical Engineering or relevant field.
Good at MS Project /PrimaveralMS Office /AutoCAD.
Good communication skills - verbal, written & presentation.
Multi tasking, organizing, team player & flexible.
